Requirements
------------

This module requires CVS Drupal as of May 2003. Drupal 4.2 will be sufficient also.

Installation
------------

1. Copy the scheduler.module to the Drupal modules/ directory. Activate the module in the admin/node/modules page

2. Run the scheduler.mysql file to create the necessary database table.

Notes
-----

Anyone with 'administer nodes' permission is able to use scheduler.

